      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2001 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. This example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance: the dual-VANOS system has been recalibrated, rod bearings replaced, and the rear subframe reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The chassis remains taut with original geometry, and the paint depth is consistent across all panels, showing no signs of thermal cycling or oxidation. A pristine, analog driving machine for the discerning collector.",
